reviewText:
Adobe Flash CS3 - ActionScript 3

This DVD was a combination of a little explanation of ActionScript 3 and some from Photo Shop. The teacher explains that I went through a named session, but it was not true and that passage was not on DVD.

I do not know why it was showing parts of Photo Shop.

I'm teaching myself ActionScripting, and this is EXACTLY what I needed to hammer down the basics.  I'm quite certain that in a week, I will sneer at the elementary building blocks presented, but right now this DVD will give me a solid foundation to build upon later.
This is probably a great DVD for a beginner. I was disappointed. A difficultly rating could help.
